Package: hawaii.gov
Title: Hawaii Open Data (CKAN) Client
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R: person("Sean", "B", role = c("aut", "cre"), email = "support@scrapeable.com")
Description: Self-contained client for the Hawaii Open Data CKAN API.
    Covers catalog listing, search, campaign finance, energy, agriculture,
    education, economic indicators, and infrastructure data.
    Includes LLM context injection via hi_context().
